The (T)ime (I)ndependent (C)hoice implementation in BAG and BAP do not
appear to be working correctly.  Consider the example
atacs/examples/er/TIC_test.er.  The events $a and $b conflict, and $c is
concurrently enabled with $a and $b.  The time is set such that t($a) <
t($c) < t($b).  In this case, TIC should produce the trace $a->$c->$sync
or $c->$b->$sync.  BAP and BAG produce incorrect implementations of TIC at
this point in time.

egm

